  </sponsors>
  <source>OSI Pharmaceuticals</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase I, open-label, dose escalation, study of the combination of cisplatin and
      OSI-7904L given on Day 1 every 21 days in patient who have advanced solid tumors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
